notes "

To add shell completions for kaf, source the completion script in your shell
commands file:

Bash

    $ echo 'source <(kaf completion bash)' >> ~/.bashrc

Zsh

    $ echo 'source <(kaf completion zsh)' >> ~/.zshrc
"
